306
00:20:57,790 --> 00:20:58,790
Miss Xiu'er.

307
00:21:01,110 --> 00:21:01,990
Who are you?

308
00:21:01,990 --> 00:21:03,510
Her Majesty has summoned

309
00:21:03,510 --> 00:21:06,670
