460
00:29:27,070 --> 00:29:28,920
No, it hurts.

461
00:29:28,980 --> 00:29:31,150
You can't recover without the medicine.

462
00:29:31,150 --> 00:29:31,990
Master.

463
00:29:31,990 --> 00:29:32,910
