465
00:29:38,270 --> 00:29:40,110
I accidentally missed

466
00:29:40,230 --> 00:29:41,630
and almost hurt someone.

467
00:29:42,230 --> 00:29:43,090
You deserve it.

468
00:29:43,110 --> 00:29:45,550
