508
00:31:41,790 --> 00:31:42,720
What did you say?

509
00:31:45,140 --> 00:31:46,320
As the Empress,

510
00:31:46,350 --> 00:31:47,590
and his aunt,

511
00:31:48,000 --> 00:31:50,260
