553
00:33:48,710 --> 00:33:49,240
Let's go.

554
00:33:50,040 --> 00:33:51,640
Let's go and see the Empress.

555
00:33:52,990 --> 00:33:54,050
Yes, Your Majesty.

556
00:34:02,710 --> 00:34:04,590
Greetings, Your Majesty.

557
00:34:04,760 --> 00:34:05,750
